description:
A - Lower Body Strength (5 Sets)
✅ 10/10 Single-leg DB Deadlifts
✅ 20 Step-back Lunges or Bulgarian Split Squats (instead of Jumping Lunges)
✅ Rest 90 seconds

B - Metcon (Modified for Low-Impact)
✅ 200 Box Squats or Slow Tempo Air Squats (instead of 300 Air Squats)
✅ Every minute: 4 Incline Burpees or Shoulder Taps (instead of Down Ups)
